quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  34,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  34,1,hamd uss khuda ke liye hai jo asmano aur zameen ki har cheez ka maalik hai aur akhirat mein bhi isi ke liye hamd hai woh Dana aur bakhabar hai
  34,2,"jo kuch zameen mein jata hai aur jo kuch uss se nikalta hai aur jo kuch aasman se utartaa hai aur jo kuch uss mein charhata hai, har cheez ko woh jaanta hai, woh Raheem aur ghafoor hai"
  34,3,"munkareen kehte hain ke kya baat hai ke qayamat hum par nahi aa rahi hai! kaho, qasam hai mere aalam ul ghaibparvar-digaar ki, woh tum par aa kar rahay gi uss se zarra barabar koi cheez nah asmano mein chhupi hui hai nah zameen mein nah zarray se barri aur nah uss se choti, sab kuch aik numaya daftar mein darj hai"
  34,4,aur yeh qayamat is liye aeye gi ke jaza day Allah unn logon ko jo imaan laaye hain aur naik amal karte rahay hain unn ke liye mughfirat hai aur rizaq kareem
  34,5,"aur jin logon ne hamari ayaat ko neecha dikhaane ke liye zor lagaya hai, un ke liye bad tareen qisam ka dard naak azaab hai"
  34,6,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, ilm rakhnay walay khoob jantay hain ke jo kuch tumahray rab ki taraf se tum par nazil kya gaya hai woh sara sar haq hai aur khuday-e Aziz o hammeed ka rasta dekhata hai"
  34,7,"munkareen logon se kehte hain"" hum bitayen tumhe aisa shakhs jo khabar deta hai ke jab tumahray jism ka zarra zarra muntashir ho chuka ho ga is waqt tum naye suray se peda kar diye jao ge ?"
  34,8,"nah maloom yeh shakhs Allah ke naam se jhoot ghrhta hai hai ya usay junoon la-haq hai"" nahi, balkay jo log akhirat ko nahi mantay woh azaab mein mubtala honay walay hain aur o hi buri terhan behke hue hain"
  34,9,"kya unhon ne kabhi uss aasman o zameen ko nahi dekha jo aِnhin agay aur peechay se ghairay hue hai? hum chahain to aِnhin zameen mein dhassa den, ya aasman ke kuch tukre inn par gira den Dur haqeeqat is mein aik nishani hai har uss bande ke liye jo khuda ki taraf rujoo karne wala ho"
  34,10,hum ne DAWOD ko apne haan se bara fazl ataa kya tha ( hum ne hukum diya ke ) ae paharoo is ke sath hum ahangi karo ( aur yahi hukum hum ne ) parindon ko diya hum ne lohay ko is ke liye naram kar diya
  34,11,"is hadaayat ke sath ke zarain bana aur un ke halqay theek andazay par rakh ( ae all DAWOD ) naik amal karo, jo kuch tum karte ho uss ko mein dekh raha hon"
  34,12,"aur sulaiman ke liye hum ne howa ko maskhar kar diya, subah ke waqt is ka chalna aik mahinay ki raah taq aur shaam ke waqt is ka chalna aik mahinay ki raah taq hum ne uss ke liye pighlay hue tanbay ka chashma baha diya aur aisay jin is ke tabay kar diye jo apne rab ke hukum se is ke agay kaam karte thay unn mein se jo hamaray hukum se sartabi karta is ko hum bharakti hui aag ka maza چکھاتے"
  34,13,"woh uss ke liye banatay thay jo kuch woh chahta, onche emiratein, taswerain, barray barray hoz jaisay lagan aur apni jagah se nah hatnay wali bhaari digin ae aalِ DAWOD, amal karo shukar ke tareeqay par, mere bundon mein kam hi shukar guzaar hain"
  34,14,phir jab sulaiman par hum ne mout ka faisla nafiz kya to junoo ko is ki mout ka pata dainay wali koi cheez uss ghinn ke siwa nah thi jo is ke asa ko kha raha tha is terhan jab sulaiman gir para to junoo par yeh baat khil gayi ke agar woh ghaib ke jan-nay walay hotay to is zillat ke azaab mein mubtala nah rehtay
  34,15,"Saba ke liye unn ke apne maskan hi mein aik nishani mojood thi, do baagh dayen aur baen khao apne rab ka diya howa rizaq aur shukar baja lao uss ka, malik hai umdah o pakeeza aur parvar-digaar hai bakhshish frmane wala"
  34,16,magar woh mun mourr gay aakhir kaar hum ne unn par band toar selaab bhaij diya aur un ke pichlle do baghoon ki jagah do aur baagh inhen diye jin mein karvae kaseelay phal aur jhar ke darakht thay aur kuch thori si beriyaan
  34,17,"yeh tha un ke kufar ka badla jo hum ne un ko diya, aur nashukray ensaan ke siwa aisa badla hum aur kisi ko nahi dete"
  34,18,"aur hum ne unn ke aur unn bustiyon ke darmain, jin ko hum ne barket ataa ki thi, numaya bastiyan basa di theen aur unn mein safar ki musaftain aik andazay par rakh di theen chalo phiro inn raastoon mein raat din poooray aman ke sath"
  34,19,"magar unhon ne kaha"" ae hamaray rab, hamaray safar ki musaftain lambi kar day"" unhon ne apne oopar aap zulm kya aakhir kaar hum ne inhen afsana bana kar rakh diya aur inhen bilkul tittar bittar kar dala yaqeenan is mein nishanain hain har uss shakhs ke liye jo bara sabir o Shakir ho"
  34,20,"unn ke maamla mein iblees ne apna gumaan sahih paaya aur unhon ne usi ki pairwi ki, bajuz aik thoray se giroh ke jo momin tha"
  34,21,iblees ko unn par koi Iqtidaar haasil nah tha magar jo kuch howa woh is liye howa ke hum yeh dekhna chahtay thay ke kon akhirat ka maan-ne wala hai aur kon is ki taraf se shak mein para howa hai tera rab har cheez par nigran hai
  34,22,"( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, inn mushriqeen se ) kaho ke pukaar dekho apne unn mabodon ko jinhein tum Allah ke siwa apna mabood samjhay baithy ho woh nah asmano mein kisi zarra barabar cheez ke maalik hain nah zameen mein woh aasman o zameen ki malkiat mein shareek bhi nahi hain un mein se koi Allah ka madad gaar bhi nahi hai"
  34,23,aur Allah ke huzoor koi Shafaat bhi kisi ke liye nafea nahi ho sakti bajuz uss shakhs ke jis ke liye Allah ne sifarish ki ijazat di ho hatta ke jab logon ke dilon se ghabrahat daur ho gi to woh ( sifarish karne walon se ) poucheen ge ke tumahray rab ne kya jawab diya woh kahin ge ke theek jawab mila hai aur woh buzurag o bartar hai
  34,24,"( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ) inn se pucho,"" kon tum ko asmano aur zameen se rizaq deta hai ?"" kaho"" Allah ab lamhalh hum mein aur tum mein se koi aik hi hadaayat par hai ya khuli gumraahi mein para howa hai """
  34,25,"un se kaho,"" jo qasoor hum ne kya ho is ki koi baz purse tum se nah ho gi aur jo kuch tum kar rahay ho is ki koi jawab talabi hum se nahi ki jaye gi """
  34,26,"kaho,"" hamara rab hum ko jama kere ga, phir hamaray darmain theek theek faisla kar day ga woh aisa zabardast haakim hai jo sab kuch jaanta hai """
  34,27,"inn se kaho,"" zara mujhe dikhao to sahi woh kon hastiyan hain jinhein tum ne is ke sath shareek laga rakha hai"" hargiz nahi, zabardast aur Dana to bas woh Allah hi hai"
  34,28,"aur ( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, ) hum ne tum ko tamam hi insanon ke liye Basheer o Nazeer bana kar bheja hai, magar aksar log jantay nahi hain"
  34,29,yeh log tum se kehte hain ke woh ( qayamat ka ) wada kab poora ho ga agar tum sachey ho ?
  34,30,kaho tumahray liye aik aisay din ki meyaad muqarrar hai jis ke anay mein nah aik gharri bhar ki takheer tum kar satke ho aur nah aik gharri bhar pehlay usay laa satke ho
  34,31,"yeh kafir kehte hain ke"" hum hargiz iss quran ko nah manen ge aur nah is se pehlay aayi hui kisi kitaab ko tasleem karen ge"" kash tum dekho inn ka haal uss waqt jab yeh zalim apne rab ke huzoor kharray hon ge uss waqt yeh aik dosray par ilzaam dharen ge jo log duniya mein daba kar rakhay gay thay woh barray ban'nay walon se kahin ge ke"" agar tum nah hotay to hum momin hotay """
  34,32,"woh barray ban'nay walay un dabey hue logon ko jawab den ge"" kya hum ne tumhe uss hadaayat se roka tha jo tumahray paas aayi thi? nahi, balkay tum khud mujrim thay """
  34,33,"woh dabey hue log un barray ban'nay walon se kahin ge,"" nahi, balkay shab o roz ki makkari thi jab tum hum se kehte thay ke hum Allah se kufar karen aur dosaron ko is ka humsartehraئیں"" aakhir kaar jab yeh log azaab dekhen ge to apne dilon mein puchta-ayn ge aur hum inn munkareen ke gulon mein taoq daal den ge kya logon ko iss ke siwa aur koi badla diya ja sakta hai ke jaisay aamaal unn ke thay waisi hi jaza woh payen ?"
  34,34,kabhi aisa nahi howa ke hum ne kisi bastii mein aik khabardaar karne wala bheja ho aur is bastii ke khatay peetay logon ne yeh nah kaha ho ke jo pegham tum le kar aeye ho is ko hum nahi mantay
  34,35,inhen ne hamesha yahi kaha ke hum tum se ziyada maal aulaad rakhtay hain aur hum hargiz saza panay walay nahi hain
  34,36,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, inn se kaho mera rab jisay chahta hai kushadah rizaq deta hai aur jisay chahta hai npa tala ataa karta hai, magar aksar log is ki haqeeqat nahi jantay"
  34,37,"yeh tumhari doulat aur tumhari aulaad nahi hai jo tumhe hum se qareeb karti ho haan magar jo imaan laaye aur naik amal kere yahi log hain jin ke liye unn ke amal ki dohri jaza hai, aur woh buland o baala imaarton mein itminan se rahen ge"
  34,38,"rahay woh log jo hamari ayaat ko neecha dikhaane ke liye daud dhoop karte hain, to woh azaab mein mubtala hon ge"
  34,39,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, un se kaho,"" mera rab apne bundon mein se jisay chahta hai khula rizaq deta hai aur jisay chahta hai npa tala deta hai jo kuch tum kharch kar dete ho uss ki jagah wohi tum ko aur deta hai, woh sab razqoon se behtar Razaq hai"
  34,40,"aur jis din woh tamam insanon ko jama kere ga phir firshton se pouchye ga"" kya yeh log tumhari hi ibadat kya karte thay? """
  34,41,"to woh jawab den ge ke"" pak hai aap ki zaat, hamara talluq to aap se hai nah ke inn logon se darasal yeh hamari nahi balkay junoo ki ibadat karte thay, un mein se aksar unhi par imaan laaye hue thay """
  34,42,( uss waqt hum kahin ge ke ) aaj tum mein se koi nah kisi ko faida pouncha sakta hai nah nuqsaan aur zaalmon se hum keh den ge ke ab chako is azaab jahannum ka maza jisay tum jhatlaya karte thay
  34,43,"inn logon ko jab hamari saaf saaf ayaat sunai jati hain to yeh kehte hain ke"" yeh shakhs to bas yeh chahta hai ke tum ko unn mabodon se bur-ghashta kar day jin ki ibadat tumahray baap dada karte aeye hain"" aur kehte hain ke"" yeh ( quran ) mehez aik jhoot hai ghara howa"" inn kafiroon ke samnay jab haq aaya to inhen ne keh diya ke"" yeh to Sarih jaadoo hai """
  34,44,halaank nah hum ne inn logon ko pehlay koi kitaab di thi ke yeh usay parhte hon aur nah tum se pehlay un ki taraf koi mutnabba karne wala bheja tha
  34,45,inn se pehlay guzray hue log jhutla chuke hain jo kuch hum ne unhen diya tha uss ke ushar Ashir ko bhi yeh nahi puhanche hain magar jab unhon ne mere Rasolo-n ko jhatlaya to dekh lau ke meri saza kaisi sakht thi
  34,46,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, inn se kaho ke"" mein tumhe bas aik baat ki nasiyaat karta hon khuda ke liye tum akailey akailey aur do do mil kar apna dimagh lrhao aur socho, tumahray sahib mein aakhir aisi konsi baat hai jo junoon ki ho? woh to aik sakht azaab ki aamad se pehlay tum ko mutnabba karne wala hai """
  34,47,"inn se kaho,"" agar mein ne tum se koi ajar manga hai to woh tum hi ko mubarak rahay mera ajar to Allah ke zimma hai aur woh har cheez par gawah hai """
  34,48,"un se kaho"" mera rab ( mujh par ) haq ka alqa karta hai aur woh tamam posheeda haqeeqaton ka jan-nay wala hai """
  34,49,"kaho"" haq agaya hai aur ab baatil ke kiye kuch nahi ho sakta """
  34,50,"kaho"" agar mein gumraah ho gaya hon to meri gumraahi ka wabaal mujh par hai, aur agar mein hadaayat par hon to uss wahi ki bana par hon jo mera rab mere oopar nazil karta hai, woh sab kuch santa hai aur qareeb hi hai """
  34,51,"kash tum dekho aِnhin uss waqt jab yeh log ghabraye phir rahay hon ge aur kahin bach kar nah ja saken ge, balkay qareeb hi se pakar liye jayen ge"
  34,52,uss waqt yeh kahin ge ke hum uss par imaan le aeye halaank ab daur niklee hui cheez kahan haath askati hai
  34,53,iss se pehlay yeh kufar kar chuke thay aur bulaa tahaqeeq daur daur ki korhyan laya karte thay
  34,54,uss waqt jis cheez ki yeh tamanna kar rahay hon ge is se mahroom kar diye jayen ge jis terhan inn ke paish ro hum Mashrab mahroom ho chuke hon ge yeh barray gumraah kin shak mein parre hue thay
